30
00:02:24,250 --> 00:02:25,320
Alright.

31
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,190
Zhiyuan.

32
00:02:29,490 --> 00:02:30,999
Are you free?

33
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,649
I have something to ask you.

34
00:02:32,650 --> 00:02:34,440
- Sure.
- You can ask him here.

35
00:02:36,930 --> 00:02:39,599
How's your relationship
with Bao Jiexi in private?

36
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,890
We're purely business partners.

37
00:02:40,890 --> 00:02:43,310
We don't know each other that well.
We merely met several times.

38
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:45,770
I've already told you everything I knew
in the police station.

39
00:02:45,770 --> 00:02:47,810
So, you guys met each other
several times in private.

40
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:51,399
Did you two contact each other in private?
Or did your secretaries make the arrangement?

41
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,249
Our secretaries.

42
00:02:52,250 --> 00:02:54,840
Did he tell your secretary
that he wanted to borrow money from you?

43
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:55,319
No.

44
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,200
So, he borrowed money from you directly.

45
00:03:02,050 --> 00:03:05,279
Zhiyuan. Falsifying testimony
is a criminal offense.

46
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,790
You were lying just now.

47
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,089
Why are you still...

48
00:03:08,090 --> 00:03:10,439
Mochou, regarding your question,

49
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,840
I can answer it on his behalf.

50
00:03:13,050 --> 00:03:13,689
The sum

51
00:03:13,690 --> 00:03:15,719
was handed to Mr. Bao by Zhiyuan.

52
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:18,440
Our vice CEO, Mr. Meng Zhengyi,
gave the order using my name.

53
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:21,050
Mr. Meng was afraid that our
company's reputation might be affected.

54
00:03:21,050 --> 00:03:23,190
That's why he didn't lend it to him
using his own name.

55
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:25,529
As for the misunderstandings
that had occurred,

56
00:03:25,530 --> 00:03:27,070
I'm truly sorry about them.

57
00:03:27,210 --> 00:03:28,319
And,

58
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,439
my boyfriend

59
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:31,049
doesn't know the details of the matter.

60
00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:33,649
He hid the truth from you all
in order to protect me.

61
00:03:33,650 --> 00:03:34,950
I'm truly sorry about that.

62
00:03:35,650 --> 00:03:36,439
So, Mochou,

63
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,649
if you still need us
to cooperate with your investigation,

64
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:40,839
please provide us with
a formal investigation notice.

65
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:43,400
Zhiyuan and I will definitely do our best
to cooperate with you.

66
00:03:43,770 --> 00:03:44,839
No problem.

67
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,399
Sorry about that.

68
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,790
Sorry for bothering you two.

69
00:03:47,810 --> 00:03:49,000
Not at all.

70
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,880
Let's go.

71
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,750
Time to go.

72
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,630
Meng Zhengyi?

73
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,880
That's right.

74
00:04:01,490 --> 00:04:04,279
Meng Zhengyi,
vice CEO of Tianxiang Group,

75
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:08,689
instructed Ning Zhiyuan to hand
the money to Bao Xijie under Luo Yifei's name.

76
00:04:08,690 --> 00:04:10,399
It's a huge detour.

77
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,529
In conclusion,

78
00:04:11,530 --> 00:04:15,049
Bao Xijie received
a huge sum on his birthday.

79
00:04:15,050 --> 00:04:16,550
And, it was in the form of cash.

80
00:04:16,930 --> 00:04:20,199
He brought the money to the hotel.

81
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:23,289
After that, Li Guangrong
murdered Bao Xijie and his family

82
00:04:23,290 --> 00:04:25,550
and took the money while he was there.

83
00:04:25,930 --> 00:04:27,670
Isn't this too much of a coincidence?

84
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:31,280
And, there are questionable points
throughout the case.

85
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,879
Was Li Guangrong hired

86
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,119
to murder Bao Xijie?

87
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,470
Or was it just a random event?

88
00:04:35,490 --> 00:04:38,609
The entrance of our bureau
was surrounded by reporters

89
00:04:38,610 --> 00:04:41,280
just a few hours
after Bao Xijie's death.

90
00:04:41,730 --> 00:04:44,230
Who leaked the news to them?

91
00:04:44,810 --> 00:04:47,920
Are you saying that there's a mastermind
behind Li Guangrong's action?

92
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,489
And, after the victim's death,

93
00:04:49,490 --> 00:04:51,199
someone incited the public

94
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:53,199
in order to end the case
as soon as possible, right?

95
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,350
That's right.

96
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:57,110
I'll request a communication
with the Interpol.

97
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,639
Li Guangrong
had been active abroad all this while.

98
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,689
If Meng Zhengyi did contact him before,

99
00:05:01,690 --> 00:05:04,040
I'm sure we can find traces of it.

100
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:11,020
